         <div type="translation" source="#irt2009" xml:lang="en">
            <p>To the enlarger of the Roman World and preserver of the public affairs, our lord Flavius Theodosius, Pius and Felix, always Augustus; the city council of Lepcis Magna set this up, devoted to his divine power.</p></div>
